additionalDescription: Studies one population. Used algorithms to annotate the song types and the note segmentation. The song segmentation has been annotated manually.
annotationsType: Individuals, onset and offset of notes, song type, nest site
description:
A high-resolution, densely-sampled dataset of wild bird songs collected over
multiple years from a single population of Great Tits (Parus major) in the UK.
locality: 703 nest sites in Wytham Woods, Oxfordshire, UK (51°46 N, 1°20 W)
name: Wytham great tit song dataset
recordingPeriod: late March to mid-May duing the breeding seasons of 2020, 2021, and 2022.
